# Sprint Goal

Transform the Video Engine from a rendering pipeline into an AI-driven cinematic planning system by introducing Timeline Intelligence, Story-aware planning and Explainable AI.

The objective of this sprint was not simply to improve video quality, but to fundamentally change how editing decisions are generated.

---

# Objectives

- Introduce Timeline Intelligence.
- Build the first Cinematic Timeline architecture.
- Expand AI Director planning capabilities.
- Implement Explainable AI.
- Introduce the Audit Layer.
- Improve debugging and validation capabilities.

