# Architecture Decisions

Several long-term architectural decisions were established during this sprint.

### Timeline-first Architecture

Rendering systems should consume structured Timeline Plans instead of generating editing decisions internally.

### Explainable AI

Every AI component must produce structured reasoning alongside recommendations.

### Auditability

Every important AI decision should be traceable throughout the processing pipeline.

