# Outcome

Sprint 002 fundamentally changed the architecture of the Video Engine.

Instead of relying on procedural editing logic, the system now generates an explicit cinematic plan before rendering begins. This separation between planning and execution created a much more scalable architecture for future AI capabilities.

---

# Lessons Learned

This sprint reinforced several engineering principles.

- Planning should remain independent from rendering.
- AI recommendations should always be explainable.
- Every important decision should be auditable.
- Timeline objects provide a stable interface between AI systems and renderers.

These concepts became foundational for later systems such as Motion Intelligence, Creator DNA and the Research Center.

